title: Sukh Sagar Anna Nagar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Restaurant chain originated in India and branched out to many locations. The extensive menu includes cuisines from South and North Indian tandoor and Punjabi as well as snacks, desserts, fresh juices, and beverages. This is a large restaurant and ice cream factory. Established in 2003 and seats 700.
